member.name: P:Hl7.Fhir.Model.Base.Children
member.summary: Enumerate all child nodes. Return a sequence of child elements, components and/or properties. Child nodes are returned in the order defined by the FHIR specification. First returns child nodes inherited from any base class(es), recursively. Finally returns child nodes defined by the current class.

member.name: P:Hl7.Fhir.Model.Base.NamedChildren
member.summary: Enumerate all child nodes. Return a sequence of child elements, components and/or properties. Child nodes are returned as tuples with the name and the node itself, in the order defined by the FHIR specification. First returns child nodes inherited from any base class(es), recursively. Finally returns child nodes defined by the current class.
